{\par The Configuration Dialog lets you customize the plug-in.  Some options directly effect the
 sound, while others only change the way Winamp provides information to you.\par\par
There are five tabs in the dialog.  Each one groups related options together:\par\par
{\uldb
{DSP}{\v Cfg_DSP}\par
{Mixing}{\v Cfg_Mixing}\par
